{"tid":159694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爭風呷醋　兩中女打交掟鞋爭男友","createTime":"2017-03-17T07:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T10:36:41.000Z","uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea370ad2bf1bcaab7b11c338ed361c4cce03b00","tid":159694,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:35:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i85mN93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi85mN93.jpg&h=342675dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】慈雲山慈正邨正安樓清晨約5時22分發生兩女爭一男打交案，一名52歲姓何男子與43歲姓顧女友在單位內，期間45歲姓林前女友上門，兩名女子發生爭執。現場消息指，林女撿起鞋掟向顧女，她亦掟鞋還擊，結果顧女被打穿頭，林女報稱頭痛不適。<br />\n　　警方接報到場，將兩名涉嫌打交傷人女子拘捕，兩人同受傷需送院治理。男事主並陪同顧女送院。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n家下連廢老都有人爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51d2d8f95703d9a2117d46f29cd16d4b4593abee","tid":159694,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:57:37.000Z","msg":"冇女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e585aaa87b7815230ffe4c425a1a7b34e2161c2","tid":159694,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T07:58:31.000Z","msg":"女呢？女呢？啲女係邊呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"513679e611b8a0f10f8e55644693b47f1fdac203","tid":159694,"uid":73722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T08:00:00.000Z","msg":"左邊條女光頭？"},{"pid":"0c80d3a957de7a42d059a703bc68b4457d978148","tid":159694,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci